00:05:48.990 --> 00:05:53.040
in Croydon, England in 1927.

00:05:53.040 --> 00:05:56.350
So, Jones had been at it a
little bit longer than I had

00:05:56.350 --> 00:05:58.790
and in the last letter
of the line --

00:05:58.790 --> 00:06:02.020
