used in the context of talking

00:42:37.290 --> 00:42:40.580
about Franklin, not about
Investigator itself.

00:42:40.580 --> 00:42:43.800
And I -- hopefully the --
this book and the discovery

00:42:43.800 --> 00:42:45.400
of the wreck site will help to --

00:42:45.400 --> 00:42:50.330
to properly restore the
significance of this work.

00:42:50.330 --> 00:42:56.020
But as the navigation
season drew close to an end,

00:42:56.020 --> 00:43:02.030
as dusk was descending
and with a driving snow,

00:43:02.030 --> 00:43:05.980
the investigators were
following along the northern end

00:43:05.980 --> 00:43:10.150
of Banks Island and inadvertently
blundered really into the confines

00:43:10.150 --> 00:43:13.600
of -- of what is now
called Mercy Bay.

00:43:13.600 --> 00:43:15.540
They -- stranded on a --

00:43:15.540 --> 00:43:18.960
on a sandbar and spent much of
the next day lightening ship

00:43:18.960 --> 00:43:20.690
and were able to get
it off and that's

00:43:20.690 --> 00:43:24.860
where McClure made
the often criticized,

00:43:24.860 --> 00:43:28.150
but somewhat logical decision not
to press their luck any further

00:43:28.150 --> 00:43:31.060
and that they would
overwinter in Mercy Bay.

00:43:31.060 --> 00:43:36.620
Ultimately, they spent two
increasingly harrowing winters

00:43:36.620 --> 00:43:39.350
with their provisions
and rations being reduced

00:43:39.350 --> 00:43:42.540
and their health failing.

00:43:42.540 --> 00:43:47.460
And when things were looking
rather grim and McClure had to --

00:43:47.460 --> 00:43:51.630
hatched a plan to send half of
the ship's company off to try

00:43:51.630 --> 00:43:55.960
to secure rescue, which would
-- is generally admitted --

00:43:55.960 --> 00:43:58.470
have amounted to a death
sentence for all of these men.

00:43:58.470 --> 00:43:59.940 position:56%
And would simply have delayed the --

00:43:59.940 --> 00:44:03.490
