01:25:17.490 --> 01:25:18.790
Sir?

01:25:18.790 --> 01:25:22.280
&gt;&gt; I'm surprised Canada [inaudible]
analysis of the Erebus site

01:25:22.280 --> 01:25:25.440
or search for the Terror
[inaudible] before?

01:25:25.440 --> 01:25:26.740
&gt;&gt; Ryan Harris: Yes.

01:25:26.740 --> 01:25:28.570
The question is whether we're
going to concentrate our efforts

01:25:28.570 --> 01:25:33.030
on steadying the wreck site of
H.M.S. Erebus or also continue

01:25:33.030 --> 01:25:35.520
in searching for the
second ship, the Terror.

