01:25:39.680 --> 01:25:41.250
which is quite a challenge.

01:25:41.250 --> 01:25:44.440
And we have instructions
to continue to --

01:25:44.440 --> 01:25:46.710
to try to locate the
second wreck as well.

01:25:46.710 --> 01:25:49.400
And ultimately we look at it

01:25:49.400 --> 01:25:53.280
as together these ships are a
